{"id":36399,"date":"2021-05-30T12:17:00","date_gmt":"2021-05-30T08:17:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=36399"},"modified":"2023-08-31T21:07:34","modified_gmt":"2023-08-31T17:07:34","slug":"dhikr-better-spoils","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/dhikr-better-spoils\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Spoils: Remembrance in mosque better than booty"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, dispatched a company to Najd and they acquired many spoils and rushed back. A man who did not go with them said, \u201cWe have not seen a company return more swiftly and with better spoils than this one!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Shall I not tell you about a people with better spoils and a swifter return? People who attend the dawn prayer, then sit remembering Allah until the sun rises. These have a swifter return and better spoils.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3561<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih li ghayrihi<\/em><\/strong> (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u062e\u064e\u0637\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0628\u064e\u0639\u064e\u062b\u064e \u0628\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062b\u064b\u0627 \u0642\u0650\u0628\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0646\u064e\u062c\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0641\u064e\u063a\u064e\u0646\u0650\u0645\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u063a\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0645\u064e \u0643\u064e\u062b\u0650\u064a\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064b \u0648\u064