y of our people return more quickly with greater spoils!\u201d The Prophet\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7996,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/13\/malik-teaching-learning-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":36399,"position":2},"title":"Malik on Knowledge: Teaching, learning in mosque is jihad","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Malik reported: Abu Bakr ibn Abdur Rahman, may Allah have mercy on him, used to say, \u201cWhoever departs to the mosque in the morning, intending to go nowhere else and to teach goodness or to learn it himself, then he returns to his house, he is like one who wages\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34764,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/23\/spoils-dhikr-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36399,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: The spoils of remembrance is Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 23, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are the spoils of gathering to remember Allah?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe spoils of the gatherings of remembrance is Paradise.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 6651 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Haythami \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650\u2026